TIER 5		The Creature		Creates an extremely powerful creature from the corpses of a target area. Creature level (hp(+500) / dmg(+60)) is based on number of corpses used up to a maximum of 4 (+1 / +2 / +3 etc). Has autocast skill (40sec cd) that consumes a corpse, heals for
								40% max hp and increases level by 1.  Thick skinned - gives the creature a 20% chance to avoid all damage from a physical attack.
								
			
